data.body:
If it has $ 0, 0 ore trucks and 0 combat unit.
Release-20170421.

On the following screenshots AI players have $ 0 but money stuck in production lines.

![ai_stuck_1](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/25843400/25773710/7cf33b20-3282-11e7-97e9-e58cb2035a34.jpg)

![ai_stuck_2](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/25843400/25773711/7f69c7b6-3282-11e7-9071-34a6c1452302.jpg)

![ai_stuck_3](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/25843400/25773712/817826ec-3282-11e7-8405-1905cec2d3e8.jpg)

A simple workaround could be something like
```
if (cash == 0 && ore trucks count == 0 && units count == 0)
{
	Cancel all productions
	Stop all repairs
	Sell all refineries except one
	if (one refinery available && one war factory available)
	{
		Build one ore truck
		if (no construction yard && one service depot available)
		{
			Build one MCV
		}
	}
	else if (one construction yard available)
	{
		Build one refinery
	}
}
(Here AI should be unstuck)
```
